      "text": [
        "فَرَحِمَ اللهُ امْرَأً اسْتَقْبَلَ تَوْبَتَهُ، وَاسْتَقَالَ خَطِيئَتَهُ، وَبَادَرَ مَنِيَّتَهُ!"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "Allāh may shower mercy on him who took up repentance, gave up sins and hastened (in performing good acts before) his death."
        ]
      }
    }
